        "id": 5045
      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-11-11T15:07:18Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "If this is all just about confusion around SkImageFilters::Paint()... can we make it more explicit what fields are in play?\n\n    /** We only look at color, shader, and filter quality. */\n    sk_sp\u003cSkImageFilter\u003e Paint(const SkPaint\u0026 userPaint, \n                               const CropRect\u0026 cropRect) {\n        SkPaint paint;\n        paint.setColor(userPaint.getColor4f());\n        paint.setFilterQuality(userPaint.filterQuality());\n        paint.setShader(userPaint.refShader());\n        etc.\n\n        ...   \n    }",
      "parentUuid": "c9bfd5e1_38793917",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 323,
        "startChar": 63,
        "endLine": 323,
        "endChar": 78
      },
      "revId": "0fd1de144f61145651dbfc530735503933e46ba9",
